From the manufacturer

Fortnite Squad Mode 4-Figure Pack, Series 2

About Fortnite

Fortnite is the action building game from Epic Games that lets you drop into a massive 100-player PvP Battle Royale or team up with friends in a co-op campaign to Save The World against a horde of monsters. Craft and loot in giant worlds where no two games are ever the same. Fortnite Battle Royale is free and available on PC, Mac, PlayStation 4, Xbox One, Switch, iOS, and Android.

Level up your game with the Fortnite Squad Mode 4-Figure Pack, Series 2! This set includes four incredibly detailed 4-inch action figures—Ravage, Omen, Moisty, and Trog—and features weapons, harvesting tools, and building materials/stands.

  • 4-inch Articulated Figures—Omen, Moisty, Trog, and Ravage
  • 4 Harvesting Tools
  • 4 Weapons
  • 4 Building Materials
  • Collector’s Guide
  • Official Licensed Product
  • More styles are dropping soon

Squad Mode 4-Figure Pack Features


Game-Accurate Design

4-inch action figures—Trog, Ravage, Omen, and Moisty—inspired by some of the most popular outfits from Epic Games' Fortnite!


Metal Building Material To Pose Figures or Connect to Make Structures

The 4 metal building materials can be used as a stand to pose and display your figures. Collect and connect building materials to create structures! Compatible with metal and stone building materials.


Includes Weapons, Harvesting Tools, and Collector's Guide

Ragnarok, Rex, Cuddle Team Leader, and Brite Bomber are outfitted with the Heavy Shotgun, Dual Pistols, Semi-Auto Sniper Rifle, and Scoped Assault Rifle—additional building materials sold separately & subject to availability.

About Jazwares

Jazwares, a subsidiary of Alleghany Capital Corporation, specializes in consumer products including toys, plush, collectibles, musical instruments, and consumer electronics. With over 20 years of design, development, and manufacturing expertise, Jazwares is a company with a progressive focus on identifying new trends and transforming them into high-quality products for consumers of all ages. Jazwares, which is headquartered in Sunrise, FL, has offices around the world and sells in over 100 countries. Jazwares’ mission is to entertain through the creation of innovative product.

Description

Level up your game with the Fortnite Squad Mode 4-Figure Pack, Series 2! This set includes four incredibly detailed 4-inch action figures—Ravage, Omen, Moisty, and Trog—and features weapons, harvesting tools, and building materials/stands.

Features & details

Features

  • Each 4-inch action figure has 25+ points of articulation and highly detailed decoration inspired by one of the most popular outfits from Epic Games' Fortnite.
  • The kit includes exclusive Heavy Shotgun, Tactical Shotgun, Bolt-Action Sniper Rifle, and Pump Shotgun weapons, plus Iron Beak, Oracle Axe, Bottom Feeder, and Disco Brawl harvesting tools.
  • Exclusive metal building materials highlight your building changes to structures. Edit between walls ramps and floors for the complete building experience—additional building materials sold separately & subject to availability.
  • Official Licensed Product.
  • More styles are dropping soon.
